## Organization Network Configuration

### Using Replicated Network Rules

This account will use the network rules replicated from your Organization Account via the Infrastructure database replica.

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| **Replicated Database** | `{{ platform_database_name | upper }}` |
| **Rules Schema** | `{{ governance_name | upper }}` |

