### Network Policy

A network policy will be created in this account that references the replicated rules:

**Policy Name:** `{{ new_account_name | upper }}_NETWORK_POLICY`

### Benefits of This Approach

✅ **Consistency**: Same IP allowlists as all other accounts
✅ **Centralized Updates**: Changes in the Organization Account replicate automatically
✅ **No Duplicate Configuration**: Rules managed in one place
✅ **Audit Trail**: Clear lineage back to organization standards